About
Jump into The Crystal Maze LIVE Experience – the hit 90s TV show now brought to breathtakingly immersive, genuine 3D life. It’s where teams run around madly, shout themselves hoarse, complete all sorts of tricky challenges and finish up in some lovely satin bomber jackets. Honestly, this has everything. We’ve just announced our ALL NEW Maze opening in London’s West End (Yes, with ALL NEW GAMES) – grab your tickets now!
Duration: 1-2 hours

    Unique experience highly recommend.
    Bought the experience last Christmas as a present for my husband and friends. Thoroughly enjoyable experience and the host Spacey Stacey was very good. Had a bit of a Richard Obrien vibe to her which added to the authenticity. My only gripe would be that some of the rooms were out of order, crysals had forgotten to be put in place and the crystal dome itself was looking a little tired. Having said all this, it's a unique and nostaligic experience which I would repeat and would love to take my kids to so I would highly recommend.
